data.description: Welcome to 32 Noble Street! This home has been meticulously maintained since its build date of 2016. Just a little insight of what this home has to offer; the kitchen boasts granite counter tops, 39" upper cabinets with crown molding and ceramic tile floors. Full baths also have ceramic tile floors and dual sinks! Primary Sweet has a nice size walk in closet. This home has abundant storage throughout! Come see for yourself!
